channel.title: Well, I'm back
channel.description:
Well, incase you haven't noticed, I haven't been posting for roughly 1 week. I know you may not have noticed because not all of you know me... Some do, Some don't. Well, what first happened, Flamed Fury, Pookey, and I where mucking about on MSN creating codes to "redesign" a persons computer, incase your wondering what I mean by "redesign" I mean to absolutly screw up someones computer. Flamed came up with a code that restarts your computer every 30 seconds... I put it into a compiler code to disguise it just for fun... I sent it to them... (Ofcourse they knew what it could do) And they had a look at it. Come and hour later, I got bored and went to compile my server after finishing a code. I compile it, and boom, my computer drops out... Ofcourse, me, being an idiot ran Flamed's code by accadent.
It was really funny, because that night, I was getting ready for my first race back. So I was trying to get my mind of it... My computer was blown.. And I was racing the next day. I fiddled around for about an hour and said "stuff it" and walked out and watched T.V. (Incase you're wondering I got 7th in my race, not bad for first race back)
About 1 week later I finally found a way to stop it. So here I am.

Anyone else find ti strange that a 12 year old races motocross?
